\c 8
\s USawuli uzingela amakholwa
\p
\v 1 Njalo uSawuli\x + 7.58.\x* wayevumelana lokubulawa kwakhe\x + 22.20. Roma 1.32.\x*. Ngalolosuku kwasekusuka ukuzingelwa okukhulu kwebandla elaliseJerusalema; bonke basebehlakazeka emazweni eJudiya\x + 11.19.\x* leSamariya\x + 1 Kho. 16.24. Seb. 1.8.\x*, ngaphandle kwabaphostoli.
\v 2 Amadoda akholwayo\x + Luka 2.25. Seb. 2.5.\x* asembutha uStefane\x + 5.6. Jobe 5.26.\x*, amenzela isililo esikhulu\x + Gen. 23.2. 50.10. 2 Sam. 3.31.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa uSawuli walichitha ibandla, engena izindlu ngezindlu\x + 9.1,13,21. 22.4,19.26.9-11. 1 Kor. 15.9. Gal. 1.13. Fil. 3.6. 1 Tim. 1.13.\x*, ehudula amadoda labafazi ebafaka entolongweni\x + Luka 12.58. Jak. 2.6.\x*.
\s UFiliphu utshumayela eSamariya
\p
\v 4 Ngakho abahlakazekileyo badabula \add ilizwe\add*, betshumayela ilizwi\x + 11.19. 8.1. Mat. 10.23.\x*.
\v 5 UFiliphu wasesehlela emzini weSamariya, watshumayela kubo uKristu.
\v 6 Amaxuku aselalela nganhliziyonye okwakhulunywa nguFiliphu, esizwa njalo ebona izibonakaliso azenzayo\x + 8.26. 6.5. 21.8.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba kwabanengi ababelabomoya abangcolileyo\x + Mark. 16.1.\x*, bememeza ngelizwi elikhulu baphuma; labanengi ababome umhlubulo lababeyiziqhuli basiliswa\x + Mat. 8.29. Mark. 1.26. 3.11. 5.7. Luka 4.41. 9.39.\x*.
\v 8 Kwaba khona intokozo enkulu kulowomuzi\x + 8.39. Joha. 16.22.\x*.
\s USimoni oyisanuse
\p
\v 9 Njalo indoda ethile, uSimoni ngebizo, \add e\add*yayikade isenza imilingo\x + 8.11. 13.6.\x* emzini isanganisa isizwe saseSamariya\x + 8.11,13. Mark. 3.21.\x*, isithi ingumuntu omkhulu\x + 5.36.\x*;
\v 10 abayilalelayo bonke kusukela kwabancinyane kuze kube kwabakhulu\x + 26.22. Jer. 6.13.\x*, besithi: Lo ungamandla amakhulu kaNkulunkulu\x + 14.11. 28.6.\x*.
\v 11 Basebemlalela\x + 8.6,10.\x*, ngoba wabasanganisa isikhathi eside\x + 8.11,13. Mark. 3.21.\x* ngemilingo\x + 8.11. 13.6.\x*.
\v 12 Kodwa kwathi sebekholwe uFiliphu etshumayela indaba ezinhle zezinto ngombuso kaNkulunkulu langebizo likaJesu Kristu, babhabhathizwa bonke amadoda labafazi\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 13 LoSimoni laye wakholwa, njalo esebhabhathiziwe wanamathela kuFiliphu\x + 10.7.\x*; wasanganiseka, ebona imisebenzi yamandla lezibonakaliso ezazisenziwa\x + 8.11,13. Mark. 3.21.\x*.
\v 14 Kwathi abaphostoli abaseJerusalema bezwe ukuthi iSamariya ilemukele ilizwi likaNkulunkulu\x + 8.1.\x*, bathuma kubo uPetro loJohane\x + Luka 22.8. Seb. 3.1. 4.13,19.\x*;
\v 15 abathi sebehlile babakhulekela, ukuze bamemukele uMoya oNgcwele\x + 8.15,18.\x*\x + 2.38.\x*;
\v 16 ngoba wayengakehleli lakoyedwa wabo\x + 19.2.\x*, kodwa babebhabhathizwe ebizweni leNkosi uJesu kuphela\x + 19.5. Seb. 10.48. Mat. 28.19.\x*\x + 2.38.\x*.
\v 17 Basebebeka izandla phezu kwabo\x + 19.6. Heb. 6.2. Seb. 6.6.\x*, basebesemukela uMoya oNgcwele.\x + 8.15,18.\x*
\v 18 Njalo uSimoni esebonile ukuthi ngokubekwa kwezandla zabaphostoli uyaphiwa uMoya oyiNgcwele, waletha imali kubo\x + 8.15,18.\x*,
\v 19 esithi: Ngiphani lami lawomandla, ukuze kuthi loba ngubani engibeka izandla zami phezu kwakhe, emukele uMoya oNgcwele.
\v 20 Kodwa uPetro wathi kuye: Isiliva sakho kanye lawe kakube sekubhubheni\x + 2 Kho. 5.16. Dan. 5.16,17.\x*, ngoba ucabanga\x + Mat. 10.8.\x* ukuthi isipho sikaNkulunkulu singazuzwa ngemali\x + 2.38.\x*.
\v 21 Kawulasabelo lelifa\x + Dute. 10.9. 12.12. 14.27,29. Kol. 1.12.\x* kuloludaba. Ngoba inhliziyo yakho kayiqondanga phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Luka 9.28.\x*.
\v 22 Ngakho phenduka kulobububi bakho, njalo ucele iNkosi, ukuthi uba kungenzeka\x + Dan. 4.27. 2 Tim. 2.25.\x* uthethelelwe umnakano wenhliziyo yakho.
\v 23 Ngoba ngibona ukuthi usenyongweni ebabayo\x + Dute. 29.18. Mat. 27.34.\x* njalo usekubotshweni yisono\x + Isa. 58.6.\x*.
\v 24 USimoni wasephendula esithi: Ngikhulekelani lina eNkosini, ukuze ngingehlelwa ngolunye lwalezizinto elizikhulumileyo\x + Eks. 8.8,28. Jak. 5.16.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho kuthe sebefakazile bekhulumile ilizwi leNkosi, babuyela eJerusalema\x + Luka 16.28.\x*, njalo betshumayela ivangeli emizaneni eminengi yamaSamariya\x + 8.40. 1.8. Joha. 4.38. Seb. 9.32.\x*.
\s Ukuphenduka kwenduna yeEthiyophiya
\p
\v 26 Ingilosi yeNkosi yasikhuluma\x + 12.7.\x* loFiliphu\x + 8.5.\x*, yathi: Sukuma uye eningizimu endleleni eyehla isuka eJerusalema isiya eGaza\x + Josh. 15.47.\x*; yona iyinkangala.
\v 27 Wasesukuma ehamba; njalo khangela umuntu weEthiyophiya\x + Zef. 3.10.\x* umthenwa\x + Gen. 37.36.\x* induna enkulu kaKandake indlovukazi\x + Luka 1.52.\x* yamaEthiyophiya\x + 2 Kho. 19.9.\x*, eyayiphezu kwempahla yakhe eligugu yonke\x + Ezra 7.21.\x*, eyayifikile eJerusalema ukukhonza,
\v 28 yayisibuyela ihlezi enqoleni yayo, ibala kumprofethi uIsaya.
\v 29 UMoya wasesithi kuFiliphu: Sondela uhambe lalinqola\x + 1 Kho. 8.41,42. Joha. 12.20. Seb. 24.11.\x*.
\v 30 UFiliphu wasegijimela ku\add yo\add* wayizwa ibala umprofethi uIsaya, wathi: Kambe uyaqedisisa yini lezizinto ozifundayo\x + 2 Kor. 3.2.\x*?
\v 31 Yasisithi: Kambe ngingakwenelisa njani, ngaphandle \add kokuthi\add* omunye angiqondise\x + Joha. 16.13.\x*? Yasimcela uFiliphu ukuthi akhwele ahlale layo\x + 1 Kho. 20.33. 2 Kho. 10.15.\x*.
\v 32 Lesehlukwana sombhalo eyayisifunda yilesi: Walethwa ekuhlatshweni njengemvu; lanjengewundlu lithule phambi komgundi walo, ngokunjalo kawuvuli umlomo wakhe.
\v 33 Ekuthotshisweni kwakhe ukwahlulelwa kwakhe kwasuswa, njalo ngubani ongalandisa \add nge\add*sizukulwana sakhe? Ngoba impilo yakhe iyasuswa emhlabeni\x + Isa. 53.7,8.\x*.
\v 34 Umthenwa wasephendula uFiliphu wathi: Ngiyakubuza, umprofethi ukhuluma lokhu ngobani? Ngaye ngokwakhe, kumbe ngomunye yini?
\v 35 UFiliphu wasevula umlomo wakhe\x + Mat. 5.2.\x*, eseqala\x + Luka 24.27.\x* kulowombhalo\x + 17.2,3. 18.28.\x*, watshumayela uJesu kuye\x + 5.42.\x*.
\v 36 Kwathi besahamba endleleni, bafika emanzini athile; lomthenwa wathi: Khangela, \add nanka\add* amanzi; kuyini okungivimbela ukuthi ngibhabhathizwe\x + 10.47.\x*?
\v 37 UFiliphu wasesithi: Uba ukholwa ngenhliziyo yonke\x + Mark. 16.16.\x*, kuvunyelwe\x + 2.29.\x*. Wasephendula wathi: Ngiyakholwa ukuthi uJesu Kristu\x + Mat. 1.18.\x* uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + Joha. 9.35,38. Mat. 14.33.\x*.
\v 38 Waselaya ukuthi inqola ime; basebesehlela emanzini bobabili, uFiliphu lomthenwa; wasembhabhathiza.
\v 39 Kwathi sebekhuphukile emanzini, uMoya weNkosi wamhluthuna uFiliphu; njalo umthenwa kazabe esambona\x + 1 Kho. 18.12.\x*; wahamba-ke ngendlela yakhe ethokoza\x + 8.8.\x*.
\v 40 Kodwa uFiliphu waficwa eAzotu\x + 1 Sam. 5.1.\x*; njalo edabula watshumayela ivangeli kuyo yonke imizi\x + 8.25.\x*, waze wafika eKesariya\x + 9.30. 10.1,24. 11.11. 12.19. 18.22. 21.8,16. 23.23,33. 25.1,4,6,13.\x*.